(Understands him well)
Ning is the easiest to win over.

846
00:23:35,000 --> 00:23:35,480
Really?

847
00:23:35,480 --> 00:23:35,880
Yeah.

848
00:23:36,460 --> 00:23:37,600
(True)
Yeah.

849
00:23:37,600 --> 00:23:39,240
(Someone's got her back)
She'll "die" protecting me.

850
00:23:39,240 --> 00:23:40,400
Why?

851
00:23:40,400 --> 00:23:42,760
(She falls for this the most)
She complimented the moment I arrived.

852
00:23:42,760 --> 00:23:44,240
(Full of confidence)
She likes my face.

853
00:23:44,540 --> 00:23:45,820
(That works too?)

854
00:23:45,840 --> 00:23:48,000
That smells good. What scent is this?

855
00:23:48,000 --> 00:23:48,800
(Deeply attracted)
Let me put some on you.

856
00:23:48,800 --> 00:23:50,080
Yours smells like

857
00:23:50,080 --> 00:23:50,960
something fruity.

858
00:23:50,960 --> 00:23:52,680
(Spot on)
Yeah, I like fruity scents.

859
00:23:52,680 --> 00:23:53,560
Do you like it?

860
00:23:53,560 --> 00:23:54,400
I like floral scents.

861
00:23:54,400 --> 00:23:55,460
(I like them all)
I like fruity ones too.

862
00:23:55,860 --> 00:23:56,780
(Giving it to you)

863
00:23:57,840 --> 00:23:58,400
If you like it, it's yours.

864
00:23:58,400 --> 00:23:59,440
Just like that?

865
00:23:59,440 --> 00:23:59,840
Of course.

866
00:23:59,840 --> 00:24:00,160
Okay.

867
00:24:00,160 --> 00:24:00,860
(Yue got it)

868
00:24:01,840 --> 00:24:02,840
And it looks so pretty.

869
00:24:03,400 --> 00:24:04,480
It really suits you.

870
00:24:04,480 --> 00:24:06,080
My heart is racing.

871
00:24:06,080 --> 00:24:07,600
It's beating so fast.

872
00:24:07,600 --> 00:24:08,480
Why?

873
00:24:08,480 --> 00:24:09,720
(The sweet talk continues)
Because I saw you.

874
00:24:10,600 --> 00:24:11,400
(Starting to suspect)
This is getting suspicious.

875
00:24:11,400 --> 00:24:12,480
The more you say,

876
00:24:12,480 --> 00:24:14,080
the more suspicious you sound.

877
00:24:14,080 --> 00:24:15,120
Actually, I have a crush on you.

878
00:24:15,120 --> 00:24:16,960
I came on this show because of you.

879
00:24:16,960 --> 00:24:18,880
(Completely fooled)
Seriously?

880
00:24:18,880 --> 00:24:20,160
What's this?

881
00:24:20,160 --> 00:24:21,280
This is my crystal.

882
00:24:21,280 --> 00:24:22,600
Touch it and you'll have good luck.

883
00:24:22,600 --> 00:24:23,560
Really?

884
00:24:23,560 --> 00:24:24,520
This one brings wealth, right?

885
00:24:24,520 --> 00:24:24,840
I'll touch this one.

886
00:24:24,840 --> 00:24:25,560
(Bringing fortune)
This one brings money.

887
00:24:25,560 --> 00:24:26,400
Do you want it? I'll give it to you.

888
00:24:26,780 --> 00:24:27,320
(Another gift)

889
00:24:27,320 --> 00:24:28,620
(Getting nervous)
Jin, I won't touch it anymore.

890
00:24:29,400 --> 00:24:30,640
I have plenty more.

891
00:24:30,640 --> 00:24:31,360
(Okay, I'll take it)
Thanks.

892
00:24:31,360 --> 00:24:31,760
Wear it on your left hand.

893
00:24:31,760 --> 00:24:33,080
It only brings wealth
if you wear it on the left.

894
00:24:33,460 --> 00:24:34,740
(Immediately puts on lucky bracelet)

895
00:24:36,040 --> 00:24:37,640
(Ancient visitors arrive)
Where are we?

896
00:24:37,640 --> 00:24:39,520
(Next Episode Preview)
This is my palace.

897
00:24:39,520 --> 00:24:41,720
(The closest ones hurt the most)
Still in your princess fantasy?

898
00:24:41,720 --> 00:24:44,380
Kneel down and shout,
"Long live the princess!"

899
00:24:44,380 --> 00:24:45,120
(Playing along with your act)

900
00:24:45,120 --> 00:24:49,080
Ghost soldier's armor.
The armor worn by ghost soldiers.

901
00:24:49,080 --> 00:24:51,640
(Wordplay master)
I thought it's ghost soldier A and B.

902
00:24:51,640 --> 00:24:52,680
Have you seen this before?

903
00:24:52,680 --> 00:24:54,840
This is glazed glass.

904
00:24:54,840 --> 00:24:55,980
(Immersed in the ancient role)

905
00:24:56,500 --> 00:24:57,900
(What happened to you?)

906
00:24:58,240 --> 00:25:00,340
(Come on, show us)
I thought you'd be good at this.

907
00:25:00,780 --> 00:25:01,980
(Nope)

908
00:25:02,620 --> 00:25:03,620
(This doesn't seem right)

909
00:25:03,640 --> 00:25:05,320
(New disguise, new adventure)
Who is that?

910
00:25:05,320 --> 00:25:06,320
The others.

911
00:25:06,320 --> 00:25:07,600
They got tied up too, right?

912
00:25:07,600 --> 00:25:09,480
Of course. We all got captured together.

913
00:25:09,480 --> 00:25:11,280
(Slightly angry)
Who told you to change my destination?

914
00:25:11,280 --> 00:25:12,520
I did it on purpose.

915
00:25:12,520 --> 00:25:13,960
But I actually...

916
00:25:13,960 --> 00:25:14,380
(Confidential)

917
00:25:14,380 --> 00:25:15,420
(Giving up)
Shoot me if you can.

918
00:25:15,820 --> 00:25:17,020
(Someone please stop this)

919
00:25:17,120 --> 00:25:17,920
I'll lead the way.

920
00:25:18,520 --> 00:25:19,600
Okay.

921
00:25:20,040 --> 00:25:21,120
Follow me.

922
00:25:21,440 --> 00:25:24,040
I found the key evidence

923
00:25:24,040 --> 00:25:25,680
at the very beginning.

924
00:25:25,860 --> 00:26:07,820
=The Truth (Season 4)=
(Viewing Calendar)

925
00:26:24,560 --> 00:26:28,560
♪Come now, players all,
let the game of reason start♪

926
00:26:28,560 --> 00:26:33,000
♪Unlock each hidden trial,
let courage spark the dark♪

927
00:26:35,020 --> 00:26:39,180
♪Night falls slow, shadows grow,
the sleuth is lost inside the maze♪

928
00:26:39,180 --> 00:26:43,400
♪Figures pass, lanterns sparse,
dark currents drift without a trace♪

929
00:26:43,400 --> 00:26:47,170
♪Wind picks up, footsteps rush,
cold laughter swallowed by the dark♪

930
00:26:47,170 --> 00:26:51,280
♪Truth concealed, the night
stands still, and nothing leaves a mark♪

931
00:26:51,460 --> 00:26:55,580
♪An unsigned letter, coded words,
the solvers gather one by one♪

932
00:26:55,580 --> 00:26:59,690
♪A broken game, illusion reigns,
who's hiding what they've done?♪

933
00:26:59,690 --> 00:27:03,330
♪Hushed voices, nerves on edge,
wrapped in smoke and mirrors still♪

934
00:27:03,330 --> 00:27:05,460
♪The next second, deeper riddles,
or the answer to the kill♪

935
00:27:05,460 --> 00:27:09,410
♪Every piece of truth
has finally come to light♪

936
00:27:09,650 --> 00:27:13,570
♪Unlock the mystery, turn the question,
let's begin tonight♪

937
00:27:13,780 --> 00:27:17,930
♪Side by side, no holding back,
follow every clue to find the truth♪

938
00:27:17,930 --> 00:27:21,490
♪The story blurs like flowers in fog,
let's begin tonight♪

939
00:27:21,750 --> 00:27:26,400
♪Search for the vanished cipher,
trace the proof, and face the sleuth♪
